title: This service may collect, use, and share location data
quoteText: Unless expressly stated otherwise, our website does not provide your information to these third parties, however they may collect information, including personal information, such as internet protocol (IP) address, browser type and version, time zone setting and location, operating system on the devices you use to access our website. They may use this information to provide you with interest-based advertising or other targeted content.
